column1: # Please refer to 10.5281/zenodo.5525214 for details on
# the dataset and the link to the publication!
# As the article has not yet been peer-reviewed
# Relative charge (QY) and light (LY) yields from internal Rn222 data using the
# HeXe setup. Included (absolute) uncertainties are statistical (stat) and systematic (syst).
# Statistical uncertainties cover one standard deviation.Correspondence can be directed to Florian Joerg (fjoerg@mpi-hd.mpg.de)
